description.en: CMI (Creative Media Initiative) is a team of 13 nations focused on building a distributed ecosystem. Based on new economic media and combines social, travel, shopping, games, payment, AI, hackproof IOT and other fields. With the goal of promoting and innovate blockchain & datachain technology for enterprises incubation. CMI designed one of the most sophisticated and perfect closed loop tokenomics, true sharing economy build on daily living necessities application. In the near future, the applications will be migrated to a decentralized and distributed storage neural network with whole new sets of protocols that’s under the CMI ultimate development roadmap, which will be completely distributed, safe, self-governed and owned by the community. CMI also collaborated with several technological partners such as MAIDSAFE, VELAS, institutional partners such as Korea KBS TV, Canadian Chamber of Commerce, top notch educational institutions, volunteer associations, etc. CMI Lab will continue to incubate or transform enterprises and integrate them into the ever expanding CMI ecosystem. CMI aimed to bring blockchain and datachain into everyone’s life.
